142 (f) Information, documents and records of the state team or of a local team shall not be
143 subject to subpoena, discovery or introduction into evidence in any civil or criminal proceeding;
144 provided, however, that information, documents and records otherwise available from any other
145 source shall not be immune from subpoena, discovery or introduction into evidence through
146 these sources solely because they were presented during proceedings of a team or are maintained
